When entering it is necessary not only to show the card to the driver but also to accompany it with the Opencard at the place intended for it on the side of the box.
With this, the driver controls the validity of the bonus.
"If the passenger needs to verify the validity of the bonds there is nothing easier than asking the driver for this information," Drápal completed.
Passengers who do not travel on buses of Circulation and do not remember when they are finished the validity of the bonus can be addressed to the machines that are expensive where the cards are reloaded.
